source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_00<tab>Memezofu is once again in dire need of reagents.
target: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_00<tab>青燐精製所のメメゾフ一等闘兵は、薬の材料不足に困っているようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_01<tab>Memezofu requires a pair of ahriman corneas to continue making medicine. Slay ahrimans to procure the reagent.
target: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_01<tab>薬の材料が足りないようだ。「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F0F201 /var>」を倒し、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>」を2個入手しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_02<tab>You now have two ahriman corneas. See them to Memezofu's hands.
target: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>を入手した。青燐精製所に戻り「メメゾフ一等闘兵」に渡そう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_03<tab>Memezofu remarks that it takes only a bit of the reagent to cure a great many wounds, but the alchemist is fully aware that an onze of prevention is worth a ponze of cure.
target: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_SEQ_03<tab>メメゾフ一等闘兵に薬の材料を渡した。彼は<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>で止血剤を作るつもりのようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_TODO_00<tab>Slay ahrimans and obtain their corneas.
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the ahriman corneas to Memezofu.
target: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_TODO_01<tab>メメゾフ一等闘兵に<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_000<tab>I am loath to ask more of one who has already done so much, but rarely do I chance to meet such a reliable adventurer.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_000<tab>せっかくだ、もうひと仕事頼まれてくれないかな？
薬の材料を調達してきてほしいんだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_001<tab>The winds of change blow constantly here on the fore, fanning the flames of war to burn ever faster through my stock of reagents.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_001<tab>ここは、ご覧のとおりの前線だからね。
いくら材料を運びこんでも、すぐに使いつくしてしまうんだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_002<tab>In particular, I have urgent need of ahriman corneas at the moment, and fear I have no other I can ask. Might I trouble you to procure these for me?
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_002<tab>そうだなぁ……「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F0F201 /var>」から、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>」を採ってきてくれるかい？
2個もあれば大丈夫さ、よろしく頼んだよ！

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_DUMMY_000_000<tab>Slay two ahrimans and acquire two ahriman corneas.

TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_010<tab>Magnificent! Precisely the reagent I requested. Its appearance is far from appetizing, I'll give you, but trust that its medicinal efficacy more than makes up for it.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_010<tab>「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E879601 /var>」は手に入ったかい？
見た目は悪いが、いい薬の材料になるんだ。
2個もあれば大丈夫さ、よろしく頼んだよ！

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_020<tab>This small sample shall suffice to synthesize a goodly amount of coagulant, which serves to stem bleeding.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_020<tab>……持ってきてくれたんだね、ありがとう！
これだけあれば、かなりの量の止血剤ができるよ。
薬を使いきる前に戦いが終わればいいんだけど……。

source: TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_021<tab>I can naught but hope that an end to the bloodshed comes before an end to the salve does.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSC910_01045_MEMEZOFU_000_021<tab>いや、そんな夢みたいなこと言っても仕方ないか。
何にしても僕は自分のことをするだけさ！
ありがとう、冒険者君！
